data.description: A truly exceptional property nestled in the heart of the Historic District of New Rochelle, this spacious Colonial stands as a testament to the rich heritage of the community. As you step through the front door, a large enclosed sunroom bathes the 1st floor in natural light. The welcoming foyer creates a seamless flow. Living room adorned with elegant French doors leads to versatile family room, complete w/ full bath, serving as a private primary suite. Renovated eat in kitchen(2021) has a convenient exit to the yard. 2nd floor boasts 4 generously sized bedrooms & full bath, while the 3rd floor offers 3 more bedrooms, additional full bath, & a cedar closet & office space.  Finished basement accessible both from a private door & the first floor has 3 additional rooms, a full bath, & laundry area. Embrace the warmth of 2 wood-burning fireplaces, 2-car detached garage, electric iron gate entrance, & parking for 6+ cars. Fully fenced backyard offering ample space & lush arborvitae trees make a private sanctuary from back to front.   Discover the beauty of living in one of New Rochelle's historical houses on Hamilton Avenue-truly heaven on earth.
